<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>FeedbackFlow | Capture Customer Insights</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; text-align: center; color: #333; }
        header { padding: 80px 20px; background: #f8fafc; }
        h1 { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        p { font-size: 1.2rem; color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .cta { background: #2563eb; color: white; padding: 15px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; }
        .pricing { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 20px; padding: 60px 20px; }
        .tier { border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding: 30px; width: 250px; border-radius: 8px; }
        .tier h3 { margin-top: 0; }
        .price { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: bold; color: #2563eb; margin: 20px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Stop losing customers to hidden bugs.</h1>
        <p>A simple, embeddable widget to capture user feedback in real-time.</p>
        <a href="/dashboard" class="cta">Start Your Free Trial</a>
    </header>

    <div class="pricing">
        <div class="tier">
            <h3>Bootstrapper</h3>
            <div class="price">$0/mo</div>
            <p>100 responses/month</p>
            <p>Basic Widget</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tier" style="border-color: #2563eb; background: #eff6ff;">
            <h3>Scale</h3>
            <div class="price">$49/mo</div>
            <p>Unlimited responses</p>
            <p>Custom colors & AI</p>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>